00:01:09,834 --> 00:01:11,767
in the talk today.

18
00:01:11,767 --> 00:01:14,067
Um, first of all, I'm gonna
go off on a complete tangent

19
00:01:14,067 --> 00:01:16,234
and talk about polygons
and how much I like them

20
00:01:16,234 --> 00:01:19,534
and we should use them more
in Google Earth.

21
00:01:19,534 --> 00:01:22,367
Um, then I'm gonna come on
to the big challenge

22
00:01:22,367 --> 00:01:24,834
of the 21st century, I think,
for the human race,

23
00:01:24,834 --> 00:01:26,767
which is global warming

24
00:01:26,767 --> 00:01:30,200
and how this relates
